
%% ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% seq_07: Org Member Approval & User Management
%% ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% Join Request flow (ProcessJoinRequestCommand)
%% NO email/password — org member approval only
%% System role change: superadmin only
%% ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor SA as Org Owner / Admin
    participant B as Browser (Svelte)
    participant C as OrgController
    participant Cmd as ProcessJoinRequestCommand
    participant Entity as Domain Entity
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant N as NotificationService

    Note over SA, N: === VIEW PENDING JOIN REQUESTS ===

    SA->>B: Navigate to Org Members page
    B->>C: GET /organizations/:orgId/members?status=pending
    C->>C: Verify org_owner or org_admin<br/>(canProcessJoinRequest policy)

    alt Unauthorized
        C-->>B: 403 Forbidden
        B-->>SA: "Insufficient permissions"
    else Authorized
        C->>Repo: findPendingMembers(orgId)
        Repo->>DB: SELECT ou.*, u.username, u.email<br/>FROM organization_users ou<br/>JOIN users u ON ou.user_id = u.id<br/>WHERE ou.organization_id = ?<br/>AND ou.status = 'pending'
        DB-->>Repo: Result set
        Note over Repo: Infra Mapper: ORM Models → Domain Entities
        Repo-->>C: Pending member entities
        Note over C: App Mapper: Domain Entities → Response DTOs
        C-->>B: 200 OK + pending list
        B-->>SA: Show pending members table
    end

    Note over SA, N: === APPROVE JOIN REQUEST ===

    SA->>B: Click "Approve" on member row
    B->>C: POST /organizations/:orgId/join-requests/:id/process
    C->>Cmd: execute(action: 'approve')

    Cmd->>Repo: findPendingMembership(id)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT * FROM organization_users<br/>WHERE id = ? AND status = 'pending'
    DB-->>Repo: Result
    Note over Repo: Infra Mapper: ORM Model → Domain Entity
    Repo-->>Cmd: Membership entity or null

    alt Not found or already processed
        Cmd-->>C: Error: Not found
        C-->>B: 404 Not Found
    else Pending found
        Cmd->>Entity: membership.approve(role='org_member')
        Cmd->>Repo: save(membershipEntity)
        Note over Repo: Infra Mapper: Domain Entity → ORM Model
        Repo->>DB: UPDATE organization_users<br/>SET status = 'approved',<br/>org_role = 'org_member'
        DB-->>Repo: Updated
        Cmd->>Repo: logAudit(event)
        Repo->>DB: Log audit entry
        Cmd->>N: Notify user: "Membership approved"
        Cmd-->>C: Approved member
        C-->>B: 200 OK
        B-->>SA: User moved to active members
    end

    Note over SA, N: === REJECT JOIN REQUEST ===

    SA->>B: Click "Reject" on member row
    B->>C: POST /organizations/:orgId/join-requests/:id/process
    C->>Cmd: execute(action: 'reject')

    Cmd->>Repo: findPendingMembership(id)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT * FROM organization_users<br/>WHERE id = ? AND status = 'pending'
    DB-->>Repo: Result
    Repo-->>Cmd: Membership entity
    Cmd->>Entity: membership.reject()
    Cmd->>Repo: save(membershipEntity)
    Note over Repo: Infra Mapper: Domain Entity → ORM Model
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE organization_users<br/>SET status = 'rejected'
    DB-->>Repo: Updated
    Cmd->>Repo: logAudit(event)
    Repo->>DB: Log audit entry
    Cmd->>N: Notify user: "Request rejected"
    Cmd-->>C: OK
    C-->>B: 200 OK
    B-->>SA: Request removed from list

